      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a \"tough day.\" i feel like i'm poisoning them. the stress, the constant mistakes... they'd be so much happier and more peaceful if they didn't have to carry the weight of my failures. i can't stop thinking that they'd actually be better off if i just wasn't around anymore.",
